snippet.title: All the Times Amber Heard Admits to Violence / Hitting Johnny Depp Audio Recordings
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Amber Heard Leaked Audio Recording Compilation /
I've compiled a file of the many times Amber Heard admits to violence and is verbally abusive to Johnny Depp in the audio recordings they made consensually as a couple. You'll also hear Amber repeatedly accusing Johnny Depp of running away, being too passive and cowardly, etc. It's clear from this audio compilation that Amber Heard was the abusive one, not Johnny Depp. 

SUBSCRIBE TO MY CHANNEL FOR MORE VIDEOS ON Depp vs. Heard and other topics. 

Here's a long analysis of the unedited leaked audio. It's funny but a bit NSFW: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P-MNGeLmlTc&t
